# Repo Name
{service-name}-service

For example:
User service repo name should be

`user-service`

# Service Domain Name
Use `doosra.com` for all service domains.\
Subdomain name should be in plurals.\
Dev server subdomain name should prefix `dev-` to the produciton version.

For example: User service domain names should be\
Production - `users.doosra.com`\
Dev - `dev-users.doosra.com`
